{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-hongyan-003__001__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-hongyan-003", "source_id": "xiaoya-hongyan-003__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·鴻鴈之什·003.1", "text_original": "沔彼流水，朝宗于海。鴥彼飛隼，載飛載止。\n嗟我兄弟，邦人諸友。莫肯念亂，誰無父母？", "text_normalized": "沔彼流水，朝宗于海。鴥彼飛隼，載飛載止。\n嗟我兄弟，邦人諸友。莫肯念亂，誰無父母？", "notes": "沔水 Chinese stanza 1."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-hongyan-003__002__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-hongyan-003", "source_id": "xiaoya-hongyan-003__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 2, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·鴻鴈之什·003.2", "text_original": "沔彼流水，其流湯湯。鴥彼飛隼，載飛載揚。\n念彼不蹟，載起載行。心之憂矣，不可弭忘。", "text_normalized": "沔彼流水，其流湯湯。鴥彼飛隼，載飛載揚。\n念彼不蹟，載起載行。心之憂矣，不可弭忘。", "notes": "沔水 Chinese stanza 2."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__xiaoya-hongyan-003__003__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "xiaoya-hongyan-003", "source_id": "xiaoya-hongyan-003__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 3, "canonical_ref": "詩經·小雅·鴻鴈之什·003.3", "text_original": "鴥彼飛隼，率彼中陵。\n民之訛言，寧莫之懲？我友敬矣，讒言其興。", "text_normalized": "鴥彼飛隼，率彼中陵。\n民之訛言，寧莫之懲？我友敬矣，讒言其興。", "notes": "沔水 Chinese stanza 3."}
